title: Missing Persons - Rhyme & Reason (1984)
description:
Missing Persons 1984 album including great songs such as the rockers like "Right Now" and the thrilling "Give", which features some of the best lead guitar on any of their songs, to the gorgeous, dreamlike "Surrender Your Heart", this is an irresistible collection of New Wave synth-rock gems.
